---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="About | NextGen Engineering Lab">

<section class="about-container">

  <!-- INTRO TITLE -->
  <h1 class="about-title">
    Building Technology That Can Make a Real Difference
  </h1>

  <p class="about-text">
    I am Ramakrishna Mundru, a software engineer driven by a simple but powerful thought — technology should not only solve technical problems, but also create real value for society.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    I work across modern software engineering including frontend development, backend systems, system design, cloud infrastructure, DevOps, CI/CD pipelines, Docker, and large-scale distributed architectures. My focus is not just building applications, but understanding how real-world production systems are designed, scaled, and maintained.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    Over time, I realized that software engineering is not just about writing code — it is about solving problems that affect real people. That thought shaped my journey into building systems that are reliable, scalable, and meaningful in real-world environments.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    Alongside software engineering, I work deeply in Artificial Intelligence, including Machine Learning, Deep Learning, Generative AI, Large Language Models (LLMs), AI Agents, and autonomous systems. I explore how these technologies can be used not just for automation, but for improving decision-making, productivity, and accessibility in real life.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    I have worked across different domains such as banking systems, financial applications, education platforms, and NGO-related initiatives. Each experience has helped me understand how technology directly impacts people’s lives in different ways.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    One belief that has always guided me is this — knowledge becomes powerful only when it is shared. That is the reason I created this platform. I want to share my learning, experience, and research so that other developers can understand how real-world systems are built and how modern AI technologies are shaping the future.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    I also strongly believe in giving back to society. Beyond engineering, I try to support people in need and contribute in small ways that can create meaningful impact. For me, success is not only about building systems, but also about helping others grow through knowledge and technology.
  </p>

  <p class="about-text">
    This platform represents my continuous journey of learning, building, and contributing — with the hope that it can help developers, students, and curious minds understand modern software engineering and AI systems in a practical and real-world way.
  </p>

</section>

</MainLayout>

<style>

  .about-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 70px 20px;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 34px);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .about-text {
    color: #475569;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.95;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  /* better readability on mobile */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-container {
      padding: 50px 16px;
    }

    .about-text {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.85;
    }
  }

</style>